title: Episode 185: TJ Dillashaw
itunes:subtitle: Former UFC Bantamweight champion TJ Dillashaw joins Brendan and Bryan on The Fighter and The Kid. TJ and the guys talk about his plans to reclaim UFC gold, training in Colorado and much more.
